# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Ketab-Yar — .dockerignore
#
# Everything listed here is excluded from the Docker build context, which
# keeps image builds fast, avoids cache-busting on irrelevant changes, and
# — most importantly — PREVENTS shipping the dev SQLite DB, local uploads,
# or the cloned reference repo into the production image.
#
# (See audits/08-deployment-readiness.md §1 BLOCKER 1: the old build.sh
# pipeline tarballed db/*.db into the production artifact and ran
# `prisma db push` against it on every deploy, nuking real user data.)
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Version control ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.git
.gitignore
.gitattributes

# ── Node / Next.js build artifacts ─────────────────────────────────────────
node_modules
.next
out
build
dist
coverage
*.tsbuildinfo

# ── Dev database (SQLite) — NEVER ship to prod ─────────────────────────────
db/*.db
db/*.db-journal
db/*.db-wal
db/*.db-shm

# ── Local-only runtime data ────────────────────────────────────────────────
upload
download
db/votes.json
dev.log
server.log
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# ── Reference / cloned repos (sandbox-only) ────────────────────────────────
ketab-yar-clone
ketab2_extract

# ── Sandbox-only directories (not part of the app) ─────────────────────────
skills
examples
mini-services
.zscripts
audits
tool-results
scripts

# ── Editor / OS noise ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode
.idea
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# ── Docker / CI meta (don't ship into the image) ───────────────────────────
Dockerfile
.dockerignore
docker-compose.yml
docker-compose.*.yml
.docker

# ── Env files (compose injects real env at runtime) ────────────────────────
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# ── Docs (kept in repo, not in image) ──────────────────────────────────────
README.md
*.md
!prisma/*.md

# ── Misc ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.next/cache
.turbo
.pnp.*
